=== Seq Construction ===
seq:    Seq.fromList [0, 1, 2]
length: 3

=== Indexing ===
index 0: Just 0
index 1: Just 1
index 2: Just 2

=== Properties ===
empty?:  empty
non-e?:  non-empty (length 3)
head:      Just 0
last:      Just 2
singleton: Seq.fromList [99]

=== Transformations ===
doubled: Seq.fromList [0, 2, 4]
evens:   Seq.fromList [0, 2]
reverse: Seq.fromList [2, 1, 0]

=== Append & FromList ===
append:   Seq.fromList [0, 1, 2, 10, 20, 30]
foldl(+): 63
